    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Savannah Ga</placeName>
                <date>April 30/66</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p>Knowing you like to be informed of every<lb/>
                <add>קהלה</add>, I take the liberty to advise you that the<lb/> Polish Congregation
                is about to build<lb/> a Synagogue, and great effort will be made<lb/> to have the
                building <sic>don</sic> by <date>New Year</date>.<lb/> I have read in the Occident a
                month or so<lb/> back, that <persName>Rev Mr S Gerstman</persName> is
                officiating<lb/> in the above Synagogue, allow me to correct<lb/> this error, that
                    <persName>Mr. S. Gerstman</persName> never was<lb/> nor will be a Revd Preacher
                never a teacher.<lb/> To keep him out of the confederate service<lb/> the Jews
                    <sic>don</sic> him the favor to let him<lb/> read on <date>Saturdays</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Yours Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">M G Joseph</persName>
            </p>
            <p>P.S. I am no member</p>
        </body>
    </text>
